<h1 align=center> Add a new PERSON record</h1>

This page allows you to create a brand new PERSON record in the database.<p>

<Big>PLEASE NOTE:</BIG> The form below asks for only the <u>minimal</u> information required for a new person (e.g. name, full_name, and PubMed name). You may specify other information (e.g. phone, fax, etc.) <b>after</b> you create the person record, by viewing the record and using the standard record updating mechanism to edit/specify additional fields.
<p>
The following information is <B>REQUIRED</B> to create the new PERSON record. Please enter the requested information in the boxes below, and then  click on the "SUBMIT" button.

<FORM METHOD=POST ACTION="/cgi-bin/webdriver" >
<p>
<b>Full Name:</b><br>
This field should hold the full name of the person, with the last name first. For instance, John Pat Dole would be "Dole, John Pat". 
<INPUT type=text name="full_name" size="60">
<p>
<b>PubMed name:</b><br>
This field should hold the name of the person in PubMed format. For instance, John Pat Dole would be "Dole-J-P.".<br>
<INPUT type=text name="name" size="60">

<p>
<input type=submit value="SUBMIT">
<input type=hidden name=MIval value=aa-process-person.apg>

</FORM>


